{
  "stem": "11998.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we didn't know what was going to happen to them, whether they're going to burn the infirmary, they're going to shoot everybody, or what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But any rate, we went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the second day, people starting getting tired and weak.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Nazis would come over, and they said, sit down, sit down, sit down by the road and-- and rest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were sort of drifting back, as you-- as-- as the group moves, you sort of keep drifting back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we found ourselves at the back of the-- of the big, long column of people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they noticed that what they-- what they were doing is they were shooting the people who sat down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They come from the back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And actually, sometimes, you take two heads, put them together, and shoot with one bullet to kill two people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was-- that was horrific.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we decided we have to get to the-- to the front of the row.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So two of us, we sort of marched quickly and to get to the front of the row.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then, you could relax, because you're slowly getting passed over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And like the-- it wasn't-- wasn't a march, it was more like a-- like a-- like a walk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Everybody shuffled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "After the first day, everybody sort of started to just floating around in this column of people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the Nazis, even they were getting tired.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they took the bags on their-- their back, the-- the-- the rucksack that they had, and they put it on some strong looking prisoners, so that they could carry it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And [CLEARS THROAT] some people started running, so run, try to get away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And of course, they saw them fall, because they shot them right as they-- as they went out.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
